optimus_cutedsl — NOTICES AND ATTRIBUTIONS
==========================================

This package ("optimus", import name `optimus_cutedsl`) is a CuTe-DSL kernel
library vendored into parallel-tree-decoding so the repository is a single clone
with no submodules. The tail-tree speculative-decode kernel it provides is the
one behind the paper's wall-clock TPS number. See LICENSE for the governing terms.

