    harness, not shipped, not used by the decode path) was made optional via
    try/except so the module imports without it.

Hardware note
-------------
The tail-tree kernel is SM90 (Hopper) only — there is no SM100/Blackwell tree
variant. It imports cleanly on any box but only *runs* on Hopper. Reachability is
gated in `ptd.engine.optimus` (capability check before import).
